{
  "stem": "1938.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 415.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't bother anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just, if you're sick, you go there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whole Poland was not too big.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was close.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was close from Grunberg to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Grunberg to Auschwitz was close.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when a lot-- and some of them passed away, and some of them commit suicide, like put their heads down under the machine to finish.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not everybody had the willpower to live.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this camp, this factory, was part of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a part of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Department, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Belonged to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a department of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And name was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Grunberg Schlesien.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By Breslau.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was very hard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the beginning, we, we received a few cards, mail, and then everything-- they, they, our parents was, all of them, sent to Auschwitz, and finito.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was finished.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we lived day by day and not too much hope to survive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were-- we knew we cannot survive this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] somehow we survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- OK, I was there in beginning till the end, until January '45.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In January of '45, they, they looked at themselves, and they decided that it's too close to-- it's going to happen, something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they decide to take us out and to, and to let us go with, with their-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so they were on both sides of women and men, SS, and we were walking.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we couldn't carry our big belongings, so we throw out, slowly, slowly, and we were left with just one thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and we approached a few countries.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was winter without shoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I can't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now people get colds.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't get-- I didn't get a cold, even.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was no shoes in snow, no food.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
